<div style="height:100px">
    <div style="float: left; width: 48%;">
      <h2>music</h2>
      <div style="float: left; width: 80%;">
        Listen or download mp3's of the band and take a look at the music we play.
      </div>
      <div style="float: right; width: 20%;">
